Description: Executable graphics demo by Suricrasia Online, released in 2020
 storage_room is a 2 kilobyte executable graphics ("exegfx") demo by blackle
 of Suricrasia Online, created for the demoscene using OpenGL and GTK.
 The demo requires a minimum display resolution of 1920x1080
